OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy this morning,
OL,6,Fscattered showers or thundery
OL,7,Fdownpours bring the potential for
OL,8,Ffrequent lightning, although not
OL,9,Feverywhere will see these. Drier and
OL,10,Fsunnier this afternoon, becoming
OL,11,Fwidely warm or very warm, though
OL,12,Fcooler and breezier at the coast.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FChance of an isolated shower
OL,15,For thunderstorm during the evening,
OL,16,Fotherwise a fine and mainly dry night
OL,17,Fwith clear spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
