OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA dry and mostly sunny day,
OL,6,Fthough perhaps the chance for a little
OL,7,Flight rain on western hills during the
OL,8,Fmorning. Feeling fresher inland, but
OL,9,Fwarmer at the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry,
OL,12,Flargely sunny and warm or very warm on
OL,13,FSaturday. Trending cooler and more
OL,14,Fchangeable from Sunday. An increased
OL,15,Fchance of rain, but still some fine,
OL,16,Fwarm weather at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
